OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,FTravelodge was contacted several
OL,7,Ftimes, but was not able to comment on
OL,8,Fthe accusations, as ITV News' Ashna
OL,9,FHurynag reports.
OL,11,FA former senior leader at Travelodge
OL,12,Fhas revealed that she was sexually
OL,13,Fassaulted at one of their hotels.
OL,15,F'Rebecca' ran one of the chain's
OL,16,Fbranches up until 2024, but she says
OL,17,Fone night shift "nearly killed her
OL,18,Fmentally" and changed her life forever.
OL,26,@yD@QOUzD@IO]
