OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,FShe had been working alongside a
OL,7,Fmember of staff one evening in early
OL,8,F2023, washing the mugs in the back
OL,9,Foffice after her shift, just before
OL,10,Fgoing home, when the coworker came in
OL,11,Fand placed his hands on her.
OL,13,F"He came up right behind me, asked me
OL,14,Fif I could feel his penis, touched my
OL,15,Fright breast and said, 'let's go and
OL,16,F*bleep* in a room', at that point I
OL,17,Fswore at him and told him to get off
OL,18,Fof me," she told me.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
