OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780553101
OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"Luckily for me, a customer had come
OL,7,Fin. So I told him to go and check the
OL,8,Fcustomer in. He was just laughing. I
OL,9,Fjust got all my stuff together and
OL,10,Fjust left."
OL,12,FAfter telling a colleague, Rebecca
OL,13,Fdecided to report the incident to
OL,14,FTravelodge's HR department.
OL,16,FShe claims they told her they would
OL,17,Fdeal with the incident internally.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
