PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780553101
OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"I didn't properly question it at the
OL,7,Ftime. I just thought, well, I'm at
OL,8,Fwork. Stupidly, in hindsight, I wish I
OL,9,Fhad, but they just told me that they
OL,10,Fwould deal with it, not to tell the
OL,11,Fpolice."
OL,13,FThe man was suspended, and after a
OL,14,Fdisciplinary process, he was sacked.
OL,16,FBut the harassment continued, with the
OL,17,Fformer employee badgering Rebecca on
OL,18,Fthe hotel reception phone line.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
