OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,FPartly perhaps because so many people
OL,7,Fmay have been involved in the process,
OL,8,Fand due to a significant time having
OL,9,Fpassed.
OL,11,FRebecca contacted Good Morning Britain
OL,12,Fafter hearing the experiences of two
OL,13,FTravelodge guests who were sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted and harassed at separate
OL,15,Fbranches after strangers gained access
OL,16,Fto keys to their rooms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
