OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,FHer incident happened only months
OL,7,Fafter a woman was sexually assaulted
OL,8,Fby a man who had lied to staff to gain
OL,9,Fa key to her room at the Maidenhead
OL,10,Fbranch.
OL,12,FThe woman was initially offered a #30
OL,13,Frefund in compensation, but Travelodge
OL,14,Fand its chief executive have since
OL,15,Fsaid they are desperately sorry for
OL,16,Fwhat happened to the survivor.
OL,18,FShe argues that if one of the largest
OL,19,Fhotel chains in the country did not
OL,20,Foffer her any personal support after
OL,21,Fher incident, what hope do others have?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
