OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780553101
OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"It was horrific. I was offered no
OL,7,Ftime off. I was offered no support,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"I wasn't even told that we have an
OL,11,Femployee assistance line, I only know
OL,12,Fwe have one as a manager. But I wasn't
OL,13,Foffered any of that. I just stayed at
OL,14,Fwork for all the time. I didn't even
OL,15,Ftell my husband."
OL,17,FRebecca said no one at a senior level
OL,18,Freached out to see if she was ok.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@QO]
