OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780553101
OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"Someone who I trusted at work one
OL,7,Fafternoon changed my life forever,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"I didn't ask him to touch me, it's
OL,11,Fdisgusting. At least somebody high up
OL,12,Fin Travelodge should have said, 'God,
OL,13,Fwow, this girl, she's been through so
OL,14,Fmuch. Let's give her a week off. Let's
OL,15,Fjust do something. Let's write her a
OL,16,Fletter. Let's do something for her',
OL,17,Fbecause actually, I have to remember
OL,18,Fthat for the rest of my life."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
