OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"If they can't protect me as a manager
OL,7,Fwho's contracted 40 hours a week, how
OL,8,Fdo they protect their customers and
OL,9,Fthe rest of the staff?"
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHer experiences led her to quit the
OL,17,Fhotel industry entirely after years of
OL,18,Fworking in senior positions.
