OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Travelodge told us:
OL,7,F"We are deeply sorry that a colleague
OL,8,Fwent through this experience whilst at
OL,9,Fwork.
OL,11,F"The safety and wellbeing of our
OL,12,Fcolleagues and guests is our absolute
OL,13,Fpriority, and we take any allegation
OL,14,Fof assault or harassment extremely
OL,15,Fseriously.
OL,17,F"An investigation was undertaken as
OL,18,Fsoon as the complaint was received,
OL,19,Fand the alleged attacker was suspended
OL,20,Fimmediately and subsequently dismissed.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
