OL,3,CFormer Travelodge manager says she was
OL,4,Csexually assaulted on a night shift
OL,6,F"We are committed to ensuring that all
OL,7,Four teams feel supported and we are
OL,8,Fsorry that the colleague affected by
OL,9,Fthis incident felt this was not the
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,F"A manager spoke with the colleague
OL,13,Fconcerned to reassure her that we were
OL,14,Ftaking the matter seriously and to
OL,15,Foffer support. The colleague was also
OL,16,Foffered access to our independent
OL,17,FEmployee Assistance Programme for
OL,18,Fadditional support.
